		<title>Updates on OpenSSL CVE-2009-3555 (client renegociation)</title>
		<link>/blog-archive/2010/04/05/updates-about-openssl-cve-2009-3555-client-renegociation.html</link>
		<comments>/blog-archive/2010/04/05/updates-about-openssl-cve-2009-3555-client-renegociation.html#comments</comments>
